        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the<strong> spicy lamb mixture</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Carefully top with the <strong>softened potato discs</strong> (beware, they will be hot!)</p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min or until everything is bubbling and the potatoes are golden and cooked through – this is your <strong>harissa lamb hotpot</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
