    {
      "instruction": "<p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p><p>Once the hotpot has been cooking for 10 min, reboil half a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>green beans</strong> to a pot over a medium-high heat and cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min or until tender with a bite</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
