    {
      "instruction": "<p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stalks and chop them finely, discard the stalks</p><p>Once the beans are tender, drain and return them to the pot</p><p>Add a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and the <strong>chopped mint</strong> and stir it all together until melted – these are your<strong> minty beans</strong></p>",
